Source: dvbipitools
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Maintainer: dvbipitools authors <unspecified@example.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), cmake, libssl-dev, libpcap-dev, libdbus-1-dev, libsystemd-dev
Standards-Version: 4.7.0

Package: dvbipitools
Architecture: linux-any
Recommends: udpxy
Description: command line tools for DVB-IPI streams
 dipirec records a DVB-IPI multicast.
 dipiscan scans and reports on DVB-IPI multicast streams.
 dipiradiohead re-muxes an Icecast/Shoutcast stream as a DVB-IPI multicast.
 dipisds announces or discovers DVB-IPI services via DVBSTP/SD&S (ETSI TS 102 034).
 dipixmltv converts between xmltv and the DVB-IPI EPG (TVA) xml shape.
 dipibim converts between the plain TVA xml shape and its BiM binary encoding.
 dipiepg announces an xmltv guide as BiM-encoded TVA fragments via DVBSTP/BCG (ETSI TS 102 539), or listens for one.
 dipitvhead re-packages a transport stream (multicast, http(s), or stdin) as a DVB-IPI multicast, with target-bitrate control and optional HbbTV AIT injection.
 dipiret is an RTP retransmission (RET) server for DVB-IPI Annex F, passively watching a mirrored multicast segment via libpcap and repairing packet loss on request.
